summary: AN ORDINANCE accepting electrical underground distribution easements over portions of Wade Addition to the City of Seattle; Kennedy's Acre Tracts; Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East; Fauntleroy Summit Addition to the City of Seattle; northeast quarter of Section 7, Township 23 North, Range 4 East; Section 34, Township 26 North, Range 4 East; Mount Baker Park Addition to the City of Seattle; and southwest quarter of Section 1, Township 23 North, Range 3 East.
